NB. =========================================================
NB. alen v length of A representation from R
alen=: 3 : 0
't c r s'=. memr y,8 4 4
select. t
case. 1;2 do. 40 + 8 * r + <.c % 8 return.
case. 4;8 do. 32 + 8 * r + c return.
case. 16 do. 32 + 8 * r + 2 * c return.
case. 32 do.
  n=. memr y,(8*r+c+3),1 4
  if. n=0 do. 40 else. n + alen(y+n) end.
end.
)

